  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Validators include a `deposit_root` in `BeaconBlock`s to vote for a Merkle root of the `deposit_tree` in the Ethereum 1.0 contract. For honest nodes to coordinate and reach the 1/2 vote threshold the honest behaviour for selecting the `deposit_root` needs to be specified. This may include constraints on the block height of the Ethereum 1.0 chain and a minimum number of confirmations.",
