    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Something like:\r\n\r\n* Let D be the set of `DepositRootVote` objects `obj` in `state.deposit_root_votes` where `obj.deposit_root` is the deposit root of a block that is (i) part of the canonical chain, (ii) >= 1000 blocks behind the head, and (iii) newer than `state.latest_deposit_root`\r\n* If D is empty, vote for the deposit root in the 1000th ancestor of the head of the canonical chain.\r\n* If D is nonempty, vote for the member of D that has the highest `vote_count`, breaking ties by favoring newer deposit roots.\r\n\r\nDoes that look right?",
